{"tid":1468014,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［集思廣益］諗到條文宣絕世好橋","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:44:43.000Z","uid":51525,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"1d45b1f6d8fa3e791dbf88b8a2c5de491c274414","tid":1468014,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係開一條中年人/老年人主導嘅文宣戰線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n先講下點解我會咁諗<br />\n出去睇放映會又好 派傳單又好<br />\n都係清一色年輕人<br />\n但係好奇怪 明明有銀髮族遊行<br />\n點解文宣個邊 反而無銀髮族戰線呢？<br />\n<br />\n成日講跳出同溫層<br />\n但係我地係無試過跳出年齡同溫層<br />\n社會成日將後生同上左年紀嘅人分開<br />\n到而家好多人都覺得<br />\n後生大多數係抗爭 老一輩多數係藍絲<br />\n自然 老人家見後生仔做文宣好少理<br />\n年輕人見到老一輩又下意識覺得好難入手宣傳<br />\n但係事實係 我地係有大把上一代人支持<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.見到一班上左年紀 甚至上埋岸嘅人<br />\n出黎搞文宣<br />\n新鮮感增加 自然會多人<br />\n<br />\n2.上一輩嘅藍絲多數都係抱住<br />\n我食鹽多過你食米 後生仔唔識諗野 嘅心態<br />\n但係銀髮族戰線就唔會有呢個問題<br />\n無年齡代溝問題<br />\n即係 generation gap 自然容易聽入耳<br />\n<br />\n3.班狗其實好驚搞到老一輩嘅人<br />\n佢一搞到 藍絲嘅老人家都會人人自危<br />\n當佢地見到同輩嘅人派傳單 都俾人捉<br />\n就會有［唔通警權真係過曬火位？］嘅思想植根<br />\n<br />\n大家仔細回想下<br />\n藍絲有無提過銀髮族遊行嘅事<br />\n係完全無<br />\n唔係因為佢地無衝擊<br />\n係因為 藍絲一派多數都係老人家<br />\n佢地唔可以用廢老去打曬一船人<br />\n自然投鼠忌器 冷處理<br />\n令好多人唔知 原來有老一輩人係企係後生仔個邊<br />\n<br />\n而呢個 正正係我地文宣嘅突破點"},{"pid":"d53362746f5fbfbd6e69e948e50e839c1c5d9f3f","tid":1468014,"uid":87284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:50:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ed307a6e7952527dda904956972bae8063430a6","tid":1468014,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n再幫自己推<br />\n<br />\n係室飽機場    係包和機場   唔係佔領機場      唔係癱瘓機場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466104</a>"},{"pid":"baf85993eb6ed30d9286d8809fe33189935788a3","tid":1468014,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0364ba6e573c55f02484d2790de6c9eebb3ff9e8","tid":1468014,"uid":189015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"186946d02cbd7cdd3151f1dc66fc7f117e70ccd7","tid":1468014,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e5400501064a12a03a50ba24e75fe748903b60f","tid":1468014,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"553dea8b017ecc93115ffd84f81b129a880a771a","tid":1468014,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:30.000Z","msg":"814照入機場，但和理非主場，道歉+幫旅客+文宣！<br />\n<br />\n[推！！！ 道歉是必須] 話錯既係政府，洗乜撚野道歉既入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4c0caba38899b7d29e7cb3b6a4424542aee8ff52","tid":1468014,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:12.000Z","msg":"唔係話年輕人唔幫得手<br />\n要退場<br />\n而係 下次帶埋屋企上一輩嘅人出去<br />\n試下新玩法<br />\n我相信 慢慢佢地自己會自發搞銀髮族文宣<br />\n直情唔洗我地幫添"},{"pid":"256108b49467ac14fe38eec6011c83637eb779ad","tid":1468014,"uid":248078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:16.000Z","msg":"我推 811 721"},{"pid":"11930f40b9a65cad021e7f38bd05a61789978255","tid":1468014,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:54:34.000Z","msg":"更加可以令上一輩人<br />\n對場運動有歸屬感<br />\n唔好到講咩年輕人主導<br />\n係香港人主導"},{"pid":"da2e978afd4ca30aaf6c7a7bc7eaf1f00ca5ad3b","tid":1468014,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:47.000Z","msg":"呢度有，長輩片<br />\n放燃燒彈燒傷警察，應唔應該自首？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDvLuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDvLuS</a>"},{"pid":"2f9b64e40515850b559ece8e9e61b965d653dcb7","tid":1468014,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:48.000Z","msg":"唔好俾班銀髮手足覺得<br />\n場運動好似好遠 好難幫手咁<br />\n下下都行咁耐 又要衝擊咁<br />\n俾佢地知道 佢地係我地文宣最大武器"},{"pid":"1a2595be592686f2f1aba993dfae4c002f4aab17","tid":1468014,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:51.000Z","msg":"銀髮手足<br />\n係時候英雄出場啦<br />\n年輕人請求支援呀<br />\n場運動有你 係好大幫助架"},{"pid":"7313ec5eb17d2d04f4155c79386580d38d201aca","tid":1468014,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:24.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門呀<br />\n文宣大突破"},{"pid":"dfe31ed5e3fd970bd86dc24f1d9938d12a12c150","tid":1468014,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"蓮登行動"},{"pid":"e1072972710650084605cb7c9178760ca715d0b3","tid":1468014,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29861a0b198f8ee5bc3f5b4d46202515d96fcdf5","tid":1468014,"uid":6589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6bd8dbece1eb5ac91fe974bfc960afdc7d843231","tid":1468014,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:59:57.000Z","msg":"寫咗段字，有用嘅話請拎去用<br />\n<br />\n我承認我們誤判 但我不與他們割𥱊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467652</a>"},{"pid":"c7e93050bb3b073bdc3be75aa41b59da82398cff","tid":1468014,"uid":296866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:09.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"69cc8fb8c678fad47274ad7a986da478a93270fd","tid":1468014,"uid":281067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:01:03.000Z","msg":"鬼在暗，我地在明，應該改變策略，全面轉為和平靜坐/遊行/一切不用帶口罩既安全活動。<br />\n<br />\n你帶口罩佢又帶口罩，係警察係自己人係黑社會你都唔知，無帶口罩佢地唔夠膽亂黎，一個電話或者記者影到佢就仆街，起底起到佢太婆出埋黎都得。手足無一個帶口罩，如果鬼有帶口罩，大家就可以清楚會留意返佢會唔會做d衰野。<br />\n<br />\n有衝擊同所謂暴力，容易失民心，保持和平不被捕，係時間要轉策略了。<br />\n<br />\n和平遊行集會銀髮又可以參加得更多。<br />\n<br />\n香港人不要再認輸。"},{"pid":"1356f96b5fa779428cfe7a903487ce9d7c9c1de7","tid":1468014,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53a1718a55f7d77d3d39dcedf490d81f4ec1ac84","tid":1468014,"uid":206538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d45b1f6d8fa3e791dbf88b8a2c5de491c274414","tid":1468014,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係開一條中年人/老年人主導嘅文宣戰線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n先講下點解我會咁諗<br />\n出去睇放映會又好 派傳單又好<br />\n都係清一色年輕人<br />\n但係好奇怪 明明有銀髮族遊行<br />\n點解文宣個邊 反而無銀髮族戰線呢？<br />\n<br />\n成日講跳出同溫層<br />\n但係我地係無試過跳出年齡同溫層<br />\n社會成日將後生同上左年紀嘅人分開<br />\n到而家好多人都覺得<br />\n後生大多數係抗爭 老一輩多數係藍絲<br />\n自然 老人家見後生仔做文宣好少理<br />\n年輕人見到老一輩又下意識覺得好難入手宣傳<br />\n但係事實係 我地係有大把上一代人支持<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.見到一班上左年紀 甚至上埋岸嘅人<br />\n出黎搞文宣<br />\n新鮮感增加 自然會多人<br />\n<br />\n2.上一輩嘅藍絲多數都係抱住<br />\n我食鹽多過你食米 後生仔唔識諗野 嘅心態<br />\n但係銀髮族戰線就唔會有呢個問題<br />\n無年齡代溝問題<br />\n即係 generation gap 自然容易聽入耳<br />\n<br />\n3.班狗其實好驚搞到老一輩嘅人<br />\n佢一搞到 藍絲嘅老人家都會人人自危<br />\n當佢地見到同輩嘅人派傳單 都俾人捉<br />\n就會有［唔通警權真係過曬火位？］嘅思想植根<br />\n<br />\n大家仔細回想下<br />\n藍絲有無提過銀髮族遊行嘅事<br />\n係完全無<br />\n唔係因為佢地無衝擊<br />\n係因為 藍絲一派多數都係老人家<br />\n佢地唔可以用廢老去打曬一船人<br />\n自然投鼠忌器 冷處理<br />\n令好多人唔知 原來有老一輩人係企係後生仔個邊<br />\n<br />\n而呢個 正正係我地文宣嘅突破點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:01.000Z","msg":"你講呢個？　<br />\n和理非第一擊 (銀髮都入嚟)】連農日報 正式上線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1411736/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1411736/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"677daa3fa0874d043d9bdbcbe49b517f48ae9c71","tid":1468014,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:05:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係開一條中年人/老年人主導嘅文宣戰線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而呢個 正正係我地文宣嘅突破點</blockquote>你講呢個？ <br />\n和理非第一擊 (銀髮都入嚟)】連農日報 正式上線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1411736/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1411736/page/1</a></blockquote><br />\n CUT 一 CUT先 唔想金剛棒<br />\n我重點唔係Target 銀髮族做文宜<br />\n而係銀髮族出埋黎做文宣"},{"pid":"7c8abcc4ddcbf0cfeae0c7f48463b29e10b5f505","tid":1468014,"uid":100267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"咩都試<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割蓆不分化<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>不放棄</strong></span>"},{"pid":"6613ea8c2fc8d230c1c6178b2efa56010242c6d0","tid":1468014,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:35.000Z","msg":"試佢一獲甘嘅<br />\n如果屋企人支持嘅<br />\n下次帶埋佢地出黎幫手<br />\n邊個話年紀大幫唔到D咩<br />\n上左年紀嘅你地先最幫得手呀"},{"pid":"8411012bf121a90f864475b468c0140a777453c6